snippet.title: Janet DeMornay is a Slumlord (and a Witch) - Official Trailer | IGN Fan Fest 2024
snippet.description:
An escape room, horror-comedy about the anxieties and horrors of what it is to be a renter in a world run by landlords. …and your landlord is a witch. Janet DeMornay is a Slumlord (and a Witch) is coming to Steam in 2024.

#IGNFanFest
